<Defs>

  <ScenarioDef ParentName="ScenarioBase">
        <defName>AOSGitz_BasicStart</defName>
        <label>Following Da Moon</label>
        <description>Da Bad Moon didnt speak to you, but it showed you things, it showed a vision of you standing before your very own Lurklair, and you liked that vision. Stealing some young Squigs and threatening a few weaker Grots, you formed a small Skulkmob and made your way to the last known location of Da Bad Moons light.</description>
